---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Marleysoft - Embedded Firmware Consulting"
  description="Expert embedded firmware consulting specializing in architecture, testing infrastructure, and CI/CD for IoT and connected products."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-charcoal to-brand-dark text-white py-12 sm:py-16 lg:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-12 items-center">
        <!-- Text Content -->
        <div>
          <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 sm:mb-6">
            Build Sustainable Firmware Systems
          </h1>
          <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl lg:text-2xl mb-6 sm:mb-8 text-gray-200">
            Expert consulting in firmware architecture and development infrastructure — not just writing code.
          </p>
          <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-300 mb-6 sm:mb-8">
            Specializing in BLE/IoT and connected products — with deep expertise in Nordic nRF52/54 chips (nRF5 SDK and Zephyr). 15+ years of experience across medical, industrial, and consumer electronics.
          </p>
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="inline-block bg-brand-copper text-white px-6 sm:px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-brand-copper-light transition-colors text-center min-h-[48px] flex items-center justify-center"
          >
            Get in Touch
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Hero Image -->
        <div class="hidden lg:block">
          <img
            src="/images/hero-embedded-systems.jpg"
            alt="Embedded systems and circuit boards"
            class="rounded-lg shadow-2xl w-full h-auto object-cover"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Key Differentiators -->
  <section class="py-12 sm:py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-8 sm:mb-12">What Sets Me Apart</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 sm:gap-6 lg:gap-8">
        <div class="p-4 sm:p-6 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold mb-2 sm:mb-3 text-brand-dark">Architecture First</h3>
          <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-700">
            System architecture and design that scales. Not just implementation, but thoughtful solutions that prevent technical debt.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 sm:p-6 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold mb-2 sm:mb-3 text-brand-dark">Testing Infrastructure</h3>
          <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-700">
            Host-side and hardware-in-the-loop testing frameworks. With experience across the full stack — from embedded firmware to networking and web services — testing solutions can span from frontend to hardware.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 sm:p-6 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold mb-2 sm:mb-3 text-brand-dark">CI/CD Pipelines</h3>
          <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-700">
            Build systems, toolchains, and release management that make shipping reliable firmware a repeatable process.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 sm:p-6 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold mb-2 sm:mb-3 text-brand-dark">Developer Experience</h3>
          <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-700">
            Development environments, documentation, and workflows that make your team more productive and effective.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Team Integration Callout -->
  <section class="py-12 sm:py-16 bg-brand-dark-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 sm:mb-6">I Work Alongside Your Team</h2>
        <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4 sm:mb-6">
          I'm not an external consultant who disappears into a corner. I integrate directly into your team — attending standups, working within your existing workflows, and collaborating daily.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-700">
          Knowledge transfer happens naturally through working together, not just at deliverable handoffs.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Services Overview -->
  <section class="py-12 sm:py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-3 sm:mb-4">Core Services</h2>
      <p class="text-center text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600 mb-8 sm:mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        From architecture to implementation to CI/CD, I help you build firmware systems that are maintainable, testable, and reliable.
      </p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 sm:gap-8 mb-8 sm:mb-12">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-brand-copper/10 w-14 h-14 sm:w-16 sm:h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 sm:mb-4">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 sm:w-8 sm:h-8 text-brand-copper" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold mb-1 sm:mb-2">Firmware Architecture</h3>
          <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600">System design, architecture, and code reviews</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-brand-copper/10 w-14 h-14 sm:w-16 sm:h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 sm:mb-4">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 sm:w-8 sm:h-8 text-brand-copper" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold mb-1 sm:mb-2">Testing Infrastructure</h3>
          <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600">Host-side testing, HIL testing, and automation</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-brand-copper/10 w-14 h-14 sm:w-16 sm:h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 sm:mb-4">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 sm:w-8 sm:h-8 text-brand-copper" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10.325 4.317c.426-1.756 2.924-1.756 3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 002.573 1.066c1.543-.94 3.31.826 2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 001.065 2.572c1.756.426 1.756 2.924 0 3.35a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066 2.573c.94 1.543-.826 3.31-2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.572 1.065c-.426 1.756-2.924 1.756-3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573-1.066c-1.543.94-3.31-.826-2.37-2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.065-2.572c-1.756-.426-1.756-2.924 0-3.35a1.724 1.724 0 001.066-2.573c-.94-1.543.826-3.31 2.37-2.37.996.608 2.296.07 2.572-1.065z" />
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold mb-1 sm:mb-2">Development Infrastructure</h3>
          <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600">CI/CD pipelines, build systems, and toolchains</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <a
          href="/services"
          class="inline-block bg-brand-dark text-white px-6 sm:px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-brand-charcoal transition-colors min-h-[48px] flex items-center justify-center mx-auto"
        >
          View All Services
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
